:0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站              <br />\n   <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d2a9fdfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"73124512d6151d028c6e008a78773099ec7a566d","tid":2252343,"uid":113604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"女朋友係唔想定冇途徑去搵人幫手阿？ <br />\n因為單靠樓主唔係唔得 不過雙方都會有壓力"},{"pid":"97075022400ea8e94e0a8c6753d3aa76af4fc084","tid":2252343,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9093ba50835e91d27e6d6fb8fa1ba54bfacb0efc","tid":2252343,"uid":156122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9aa2447134a0cb17f9995b0c8eb14075f03c82db","tid":2252343,"uid":113604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"點樣人格分裂法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:02:52.000Z","msg":"有時突然變咗另一個人咁<br />\n但只係幾秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:40:42.000Z","msg":"佢係咪BPD 同我好似"},{"pid":"f74add1ee2ce518a355ae4f0f3253a9491ff6634","tid":2252343,"uid":114186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24131b9d7f6b3a70c5ed78779f8fbb0489ab379f","tid":2252343,"uid":156122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25963e50d2463fe15e5c0bf74f6ee91ba963c756","tid":2252343,"uid":358503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"點樣變第2個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會有啲說話唔啱聽<br />\n但佢唔想發你脾氣所以變咗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T17:00:01.000Z","msg":"唔